               <provenance>Lǝǧ Gabra Kidān is mentioned as the owner in
                     Additio 1 with other members of his family. Their names also appear in the
                     supplication formulas e.g., 4rb, 11va, 28vb, 34ra,
                     35v.
 The name of a different person Gabra Śǝllāse is written in a recent
                     hand, in strong red ink, on 27vb, 28va; his name
                     is also crudely written on fols.1r, 2r, 40v.</provenance></history>

